DataName: Stem diameter (DBH) second largest at site
Reference: unpub.
Comment: Diameter at breast height of second largest stem if its dbh is at least 1/3 of dbh1.

Reference: unpub.
Comment: Diameter at breast height (cm; measured at 1.3 m height) of largest stem. Reported as 0.1 cm for stems too small to measure at 1.3 m height. Only measured for woody plant species with a growth form that can potentially reach 1.3 m height. Typically, only recorded for intensively-sampled individuals.
